item.title: 贝克曼AU680
item.description:
接口说明

仪器厂商 贝克曼AU680
 仪器型号 贝克曼AU680
通讯方式 双向
 仪器类型 生化
医院名称
程序名称 MI.MIFAU680
终端服务器地址 终端服务器端口号

仪器上接口标示和接口类型

  1. 接口类型：串口
  2. 连接方式：ASTM协议

仪器接口说明

  • 仪器配置对于接口影响较大，因此要根据实际的配置情况对应接口，本接口按照以下配置进行测试
  • 贝克曼AU680对于条码号长度敏感，不同长度的条码号对于仪器的接口有影响，本接口测试为10位条码
  • 通道号为3位061类似通道号，通道号在仪器上配置，非固定通道号，经测试与格式配置中在线测试编号数字有关系

串口盒子配置

  • 波特率： 9600
  • 数据位：7
  • 停止位： 1
  • 校验位： N

/// 名称: MI.MIFAU680
/// 描述: AU 680仪器接口
/// 通讯方式：双向
/// 编写者:liuzf
/// 编写日期: 20150827
/// 
MIFAU680(mi) 
  s mi=$g(mi) 
  i '$l(mi) q
  s ^TMPMACHDATA1(mi,11)=mi
  s ItemDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),12) //项目分隔符
  s ResultDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),13) //结果分隔符
  s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),14) //抗生素分隔符
  s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),15) //药敏结果分隔符
  s Port="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),17)  //端口号
  //控制字符
  SET $ZTRAP="ErrHandler"
  s stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),nak=$c(15),etb=$c(23),end=$c(5)
  s (epis,result,date,time,QC)=""
  s ^TMPMACHDATA1(mi,10)=mi
  i $$Start^MI.MIF000(mi) q
  f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(mi) q
  s ^TMPMACH10(mi,50)=$h
  c Port
  q
 
Main 
 s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(mi,stx,etb_","_etx) q:'$l(record)
 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
 ;d ACK                                    
 //上传项目 
 //R 00002803 0169    1003007"
 //R 00000201 0059□□□□□□□□□□A010001815
 //D 00000107 E207           E0970137.1r 098002.39r 0990105.3r "
 //S 003001 0173             1002947    E001002003004015"
 //S□000201□0059□□□□□□□□□□A010001815□□□□E027
 //S□001101□0001□□□□□□□□□□1000000028□□□□E097098
 //S□000801□0059□□□□□□□□□□A010009152□□□□E0270
 //S□001101□0001□□□□□□□□□□1000000028□□□□E097098
 //D□000508□0048□□□□□□□□□□□□A0139941□□□□E018009.56r□
 //R□00000801□0059□□□□□□□□□□A010009152
 //S 0000105 0007    A0060359    E002010013014015016045049054058092097098099
 s texttype=$e(record,1,2)
 i texttype="RH" d  q
 .s epis=$tr($e(record,16,39)," ") 
 .;s Pos=$e(record,5,41)
 .s Pos=$e(record,5,39)
 .s RackNo=$e(Pos,1,6)
 .d ReRequest
 i texttype="R " d  q
 .s epis=$tr($e(record,14,39)," ") 
 .s Pos=$e(record,3,41)
 .s RackNo=$e(Pos,1,6)
 .///标本核收
 .;s retVal=$$ReceiveLabno^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,RackNo)
 .;i retVal'=1 Quit
 .d SendTestItem
 //采集结果 
 i texttype="D "!(texttype="d ")!(texttype="DQ")!(texttype="DH")!(texttype="dH") d  q
 .s block=$e(record,40)
 .s temstr=record
 .f temi=1:1:$l(temstr,etb) d
 ..s record=$p(temstr,etb,temi)
 ..i $e(record,1)=$c(2) s record=$p(record,$c(2),2)
 ..i '$l(record) q
 ..///D 00000101 E003                        E15    288.5  
 ..///D 00003007 0153    1003005    E0010007.1r 0020016.8r 0030135.1r 0040017.6r 015006.21r " 
 ..// D□00□□□□02□P002□□□□□□□□□□E030007032□□□□E0600053.4r□
 ..// D□00000608□0063□□□□□□□□□□A010017861□□□□E019002.17r□020004.29r□022001.15r□023001.97r□024001.40r□025000.95r□0320068.4r□033405.67r□043001.01r□044002.05r□045002.36r□092001.18r□095001.17r□097000135r□0980006.9r□099000103r□
 ..s res=$E(record,29,$l(record))
 ..s (sample,epis,surname,result,date,time,QC)=""
 ..s epis=$tr($e(record,14,25)," ") 
 ..I '$L(epis) D
 ...S epis=$tr($e(record,10,13)," ")
 ..//流水号转条码号
 ..i $l(epis)<5,epis'["E"  d
 ...s WorkGroupMachienDR=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),6)
 ...i '$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",$zd(+$h,8),WorkGroupMachienDR," "_epis)) q
 ...s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",$zd(+$h,8),WorkGroupMachienDR," "_epis,""))
 ...s VisitNumberDR=$lg(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR),2)
 ...s epis=$lg(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR),2)

 ..i texttype="DQ" d
 ...s epis=$tr($e(record,24,27)," ")
 ...s epis="Q"_epis
 ...;s QC=$e(record,45)
 ...;s QC="QC"_QC,epis=QC 
 ...;s QC="\"_epis
 ...;s res=$e(record,41,$l(record))
 ..f j=1:14:$l(res) s rec=$e(res,j,j+13) q:rec=""  d
 ...s code=$e(rec,1,3),resx=+$tr($e(rec,4,14)," "),flag=$tr($e(rec,13,14)," ")
 ...S:resx?1".".N resx="0"_resx
 ...s resx=$tr(resx,"GM")
 ...i $e(resx,1,2)="-." s resx="-0."_$e(resx,3,$l(resx))
 ...s result=result_code_ResultDeli_resx_ItemDeli
 .i $l(epis),$l(result) d //block="E",
 ..d Save^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,result,date,time,QC)
 ..s (sample,epis,surname,result,date,time,QC)=""
 q
 
LOAD ;
 i $d(^TMIF(mi,10)) k ^TMIF(mi,10)
 i $d(^TMP($zn,mi,"LL")) k ^TMP($zn,mi,"LL")
 //d loadlist^MIF000(mi)
 s (sx,line)="" f  s sx=^TMP($zn,mi,"LL1",sx) q:sx=""  d 
 .s send=^(sx)
 .s data="S "_send_data
 .s line=$o(^TMIF(mi,10,""),-1)+1,^TMIF(mi,10,line)=data
 q   
 ; send 'ack' to instrument
ACK  
  h 0.5
  s ack=$c(6)
  w ack,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"ACK","H-->M")
  q  
 ; send string to instrument
SAVE(mi) ; Create LoadList Records
 s (epis,samno,str)=""
 s epis=^TMP("MIF000",$j,"LL","EPISODE"),epis=$j($p(epis,$c(1),1),20)
 s samno=+^TMP("MIF000",$j,"LL","SAMPLE")
 s dumy=$j(" ",4),blockno="E"
 s sex=$j(" ",1),age=$j(" ",3),month=$j(" ",2),pat=$j(" ",60)
 s patinfo=sex_age_month_pat
 s (z,test)="" f  s z=$o(^TMP("MIF000",$j,"LL","TEST",z)) q:z=""  s test=test_z
 s str=epis_dummy_blockno_patinfo_test
 s ^TMP("MIFCL900",mi,"LL",samno)=str
 q   
SEND ;
 s (x,str)="" f  s x=$o(^TMIF(mi,10,x)) q:x=""  d
 .s str=^(x) ;;f i=1:1:2 d q:ok
 .w stx_str_etx,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str,"H-->M")
 s str="SE00"
 w stx_str_etx,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str,"H-->M")
 k ^TMP($zn,mi,"LL1")
 q
 //d SendTestItem^MI.MIFAU680
SendTestItem
 s ItemChannel=""
 ;s epis="$$SearchTestItem^MI.MIFAU680("A010017297")"
 s ItemChannel=$$SearchTestItem(epis)
 ;s ItemChannel="002010013014015016045049054058092097098099"
 ;s str="S "_Pos_"   "_" E"_ItemChannel
 s str="S "_Pos_"   "_" E"_ItemChannel
 //s str="S "_Pos_"   "_" E008005009"  //ItemChannel
 //s str="S 001101 0002          1000000030    E005008009"
 w stx_str_etx,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str,"H-->M")
 ;s str="SE"
 ;w stx_str_etx,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str,"H-->M")
 ;r *a:5 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(a)=ack:"ACK",$c(a)=nak:"NAK",1:$c(a)),"H<--M")
 s epis=""
 q


ReRequest 
 s ItemChannel=""
 s str="SH"_Pos_"   "_" E"_ItemChannel
 w stx_str_etx,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str,"H-->M")
 s str="SE"
 w stx_str_etx,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,str,"H-->M")
 r *a:5 d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$s($c(a)=ack:"ACK",$c(a)=nak:"NAK",$c(a)=stx:"NAK",1:$c(a)),"H<--M") i $c(a)=stx w etx d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,etx,"H-->M")
 q   
SearchTestItem(epis)
  S tcx="",tc=""
  d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,epis)
  i $d(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,epis)) f N=1:1 s tc=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,epis,tc)) q:tc=""  d
    .I $L(tc)=2 D
    ..S tc="0"_tc
    .I $L(tc)=3 D
    ..S tc=tc
    .I $L(tc)>=4 D
    ..S tc=$E(tc,2,4)
    .s tcx=tcx_tc
    Q tcx
   
ErrHandler
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,$TR($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE,"Runtime Error")
  h 10
    Q
  
  
GetTestItem(mi)
  S mi=$G(mi)
  S tc="",tcs=""
  F {
     S tc=$O(^TMIF(mi,2,tc))
     Q:'$L(tc)
  
     S data=$G(^TMIF(mi,2,tc))
     S flag=$P(data,"\",3)
     Continue:flag'="Y"
     S chl=$P(data,"\",1)
   
     I $L(chl)>3 {
       S chl=$E(chl,2,$L(chl)) 
     }
     S tcs=tcs_chl
  }
  Q tcs

通讯方式 双向 仪器类型 微生物
医院名称
程序名称 MI.MIFDL96A
终端服务器地址 终端服务器端口号

仪器上接口标示和接口类型

  1. 接口类型：通过监听连接仪器
  2. 连接方式：数据库类型为mysql

仪器接口说明

  • 先通过^LISTMPWSW获取细菌，抗生素，专家规则数据，通过细菌通道为索引组装保存数据
  • 保存细菌数据后未生成对应的报告和鉴定树导致专家规则无法保存，调用 try{d ##class(IDP.WS.BLL.DHCIDPResult).GetReportIDPTreeJSONStream(ReportDR, "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "")}catch{}方法生成鉴定树，随后进行保存专家规则
  • 通过sql插入标本信息达成双向

  • 数据位：8
  • 停止位： 1

/// [{"MachID":"#RowID","Type":"DataBase","UpTime":"3000","Address":"DSN=DL96A","UpCDF":"","UpREF":"","DealProcess":"MI.MIFDL96A","Para":"SELECT * FROM lis_result  WHERE DATE(UpdateDate) = CURDATE()#ID#","PreDealClass":"PreDeal.DealDemoM,PreDeal","UPPreDealClass":"PreDeal.DealDemoM,PreDeal"}]
Class MI.MIFDL96A Extends %RegisteredObject
{

/// D ##class(MI.MIFDL96E02).fileMTHD("22","4185~33122416~~~□肺炎链球菌(S.pneumoniae)□G+球菌□□[spn]□(优势菌2)~~~~~A;PEN;;＝8;耐药;;B;CLI;;≥8;耐药;;A;SXT;;≥8/152;耐药;;B;CRO;;＝1;敏感;;A;ERY;;≥16;耐药;;B;VA;;≤1;敏感;;B;LEV;;＝2;敏感;;B;TET;;＝32;耐药;;B;MRP;;≤0.25;敏感;;C;CXM;;≥4;耐药;;C;RIF;;≤0.5;敏感;;C;AMC;;≤1.0/0.5;敏感;;C;LNZ;;≤2;敏感;;~~~~~对左氧氟沙星敏感的菌株可预报其对吉米沙星和莫西沙星敏感。[13][10]对四环素敏感的菌株对多西环素和米诺环素也敏感。[13][10]利福平不单独用于抗菌治疗。[13][10]红霉素可预报阿奇霉素、克拉霉素和地红霉素的敏感和耐药性。[13][10]~~~~普通细菌培养+药敏~2020-12-25□8:33:23~2020-12-27□8:33:23~1~","", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "")
/// d ##class(MI.MIFDL96AN).fileMTHD("56",$g(^YHR("WSWQC")))
ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record, epis, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
    s mi=$g(mi)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    i '$l(record) q ""
	s ItemDeli=$c(92) //项目分隔符92
	s ResultDeli=$c(44) //结果分隔符44
	s AntDeli="]" //抗生素分隔符]

/// w ##class(MI.MIFDL96A).SaveZJGZ("WX250104003","56",1,"1、MDR：多重耐药菌株。 2、QNR-ECO：喹诺酮类耐药的大肠埃希菌。 3、产ESBL株：产超广谱β-内酰胺酶菌株。 4、CTX-CRO-R-ECO：头孢噻肟或头孢曲松耐药的大肠埃希菌。 5、治疗非复杂泌尿道感染的头孢唑林折点是基于1g q12h的给药方案。 6、仅肠沙门菌伤寒血清型和志贺菌属具有阿奇霉素的临床推荐折点。 7、亚胺培南的折点基于500mg q6h或1g q8h的给药方案。 8、多黏菌素B应与一种或多种活性抗生素联合使用，建议咨询感染诊治专家。 9、氨苄西林的结果可用于预报阿莫西林的敏感性。 10、头孢唑啉的结果可预报非复杂性的泌尿系统感染的大肠埃希菌对口服头孢拉定、头孢地尼、头孢克罗、头孢丙烯、头孢泊肟、头孢呋辛的敏感性。 11、厄他培南的折点基于1g qd的给药方案。 12、对于肺炎即使黏菌素或多黏菌素B全身给药，亦很可能无效。 13、头孢西丁的折点基于至少8g qd的给药方案。 14、美罗培南的折点基于1g q8h的给药方案。 15、头孢呋辛（注射）的折点基于1.5g q8h的给药方案。 16、环丙沙星折点基于静脉注射400mg q12h或口服500mg q12h给药方案。 17、多黏菌素B应给予负荷剂量和最大推荐剂量。 18、头孢噻肟的折点基于1g q8h的给药方案。 19、治疗非复杂泌尿道以外感染的头孢唑林折点是基于2g q8h的给药方案。 20、此报告采用的折点标准来源为CLSIM100 2024，其中哌拉西林/他唑巴坦为CLSIM100 2021，头孢哌酮/舒巴坦为CHINET技术要求 2022，替加环素为EUCAST 2018，阿米卡星、庆大霉素为CLSIM100 2022。")
ClassMethod SaveZJGZ(epis, mi, code, ExpertRules)
{
	s epis=$g(epis),mi=$g(mi),ExpertRules=$g(ExpertRules)
	s episData=$$GetEpisByLabno(mi,epis)
	s epis=$p(episData,"^",1)
	s WGM=$p(episData,"^",2)
	s ReportDR=$p(episData,"^",3)
	s TestCodeDR=..GerTestCodeDR(mi,code)

	i $l(ReportDR) d
	.s IDPResultDR=$o(^dbo.IDPResultI("IndexIDPElement",ReportDR,2,""))
	.i '$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberTestSetI("IndexReportID",ReportDR)) q
	.i '$l(TestCodeDR) q
	.try{d ##class(IDP.WS.BLL.DHCIDPResult).GetReportIDPTreeJSONStream(ReportDR, "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "", "")}catch{}

	i '$l(mi) q 0
	i '$l(epis) d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"流水号不能为空","保存检测结论返回")  q 0
	//报告可能核收到微生物培养的四个小组
	s sc=0
	s transmitDate="" f  s transmitDate=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGM,""_epis,transmitDate)) q:transmitDate=""  d
	.s ReportDR="" f  s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNo",WGM,""_epis,transmitDate,ReportDR)) q:ReportDR=""  d 
	..//IndexReportItem On (VisitNumberReportDR, TestCodeDR)
	..i '$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportResultI("IndexReportItem",ReportDR,TestCodeDR)) q
	..s ResultDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportResultI("IndexReportItem",ReportDR,TestCodeDR,""))
	..s objRep=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReportResult).%OpenId(ResultDR)
	..s EXPRlues=objRep.ExpertRule
	..i EXPRlues=ExpertRules q  //专家规则不再变化，不存
	..s objRep.ExpertRule=ExpertRules
	..s sc=objRep.%Save()
	..i ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)) d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"保存检测结论失败","保存检测结论失败返回") q
	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,ExpertRules,"保存检测结论成功返回")
	q sc


GetEpisByLabno(mi,Epis)
	//通过检验号获取流水号
	;Index IndexVisitNumber On VisitNumber [ SqlName = Index_VisitNumber, Type = index, Unique ];
	;Index IndexReportID On (VisitNumberDR, WorkGroupMachineDR, OrderNo) [ SqlName = Index_ReportID, Type = index, Unique ];
	s ret="",mi=$g(mi),Epis=$g(Epis),ReportDR=""
	i '$l(mi) q Epis
	i '$l(Epis) q Epis
	s WGMachineID=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Epis)) d
	.s VisitnumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",Epis,""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR)) d
	..s WGMachineID=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1)) d
	..s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitnumberDR,WGMachineID,1,""),-1)
	..s ret=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),8)

	i $l(ret) q ret_"^"_WGMachineID_"^"_ReportDR
	i '$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNoNew",Epis)) q ret_"^"_WGMachineID_"^"_ReportDR
	s WGMachineID=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNoNew",Epis,""))
	s TransmitDate=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNoNew",Epis,WGMachineID,""))
	s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexMicNoNew",Epis,WGMachineID,TransmitDate,""))
	s ret=Epis
	q ret_"^"_WGMachineID_"^"_ReportDR
}

/// D ##class(MI.MIFLISMonitorTest)SaveImageMTHD("7","9999", "","175")
/// mi:仪器
/// epis：流水号，如果是监听图片模式该位置放图片名称，自己在保存前提取流水
/// ImageClass:图片类别，如果是监听图片模式该位置放图片名称，自己在保存前提取图片类型
/// FileName:保存在文件服务的相对路径，默认不动
/// FullName:文件全路径，如果是监听图片模式该位置放图片全路径名称，满足有的图片名称无法得到流水和图片类别的情况
ClassMethod SaveImageMTHD(mi, epis, ImageClass, FileName, FullName, SaveImageRetName, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
	//通过OtherPara配置取图的在这里通过epis和ImageClass的图片名字提取出流水号和图片类别
    s mi=$g(mi)
    s epis=$g(epis)
    s ImageClass=$g(ImageClass)
    s FileName=$g(FileName)
    s FullName=$g(FullName)
    s SaveImageRetName=$g(SaveImageRetName)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Trace(mi,epis_":"_ImageClass_":"_FileName,"H<--M")
    s (ReceiveDate, ImageOrder, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)=""
    //加上当前时间，防止浏览器缓存
    s FileName=FileName_"?"_$p($h,",",2)
    //OtherPara用^分隔第四位指定SaveImageRetName的话在这里改FileName为新名称。同时让方法返回新图片名字
    s NewFileName=""
    i SaveImageRetName="SaveImageRetName" d
    .//图片新名字
    .;s NewFileName=epis_"-"_ImageClass_"-"
    .//路径新名字
    .s NewPathName=""
    .s SPLen=$l(FileName,"/")
    .f ii=1:1:SPLen d
    ..i ii<SPLen d
    ...s NewPathName=NewPathName_$p(FileName,"/",ii)_"/"
    ..i ii=SPLen d
    ...s NewFileName=NewFileName_$p(FileName,"/",ii)
    .s NewPathName=NewPathName_NewFileName
    .s FileName=NewPathName
  
    //最后返回NewFileName
    s ret=##Class(MI.Common.MachineResult).SaveImage(ReceiveDate, epis, ImageClass, ImageOrder, FileName, mi, Caption, DisplayRatio, Height, Width, Sequence)
    //返回值控制图片名称模式
    i SaveImageRetName="SaveImageRetName" d
    .s ret=NewFileName
    q ret
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }
    Else      { 
        Set Row=^CacheTemp(repid,ind)
    }
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

/// w ##Class(MI.MIFLISMonitorTest).GetLabnoInfo(6,1001367)
ClassMethod GetLabnoInfo(mi, labno) As %String
{
    s mi=$g(mi),labno=$g(labno)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    //获取项目通道号
    d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(mi,labno)
    s tcx=""
    s chl="" f  s chl=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno,chl)) q:chl=""  d
    .s tcx=tcx_chl_"+"
    s tcx=$e(tcx,1,$l(tcx)-1)
    k ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,mi,labno)
    i $l(tcx) s tcx=labno_","_tcx_"|"
    q tcx
}

/// w ##Class(MI.MIFDL96A2).GetEPIS("56","9000000324")
ClassMethod GetEPIS(mi, labno) As %String
{
    //IndexReportID On (VisitNumberDR, WorkGroupMachineDR, OrderNo)
    s labno = $g(labno),mi=$g(mi)
    i $l(labno)=0 q ""
    s EPIS=""
    s VisitNumberDR = $o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
    i '$l(VisitNumberDR) q ""
    s WGMDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
    i $l(WGMDR),'$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WGMDR)) d
    .s WGMDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,""))
    i '$l(WGMDR) q ""
    s OrderNo=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WGMDR,""))
    s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WGMDR,OrderNo,""))
    s EPIS=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),8)
    s AcceptDate=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),9)
    s AcceptDate=$e(AcceptDate,1,4)_"-"_$e(AcceptDate,5,6)_"-"_$e(AcceptDate,7,8)
    s AcceptTime=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),10)
    S AcceptDT=AcceptDate_" "_$zt(AcceptTime,1)
    q EPIS_"^"_AcceptDT
}

/// w ##Class(MI.MIFDL96A2).GetPatInfo("40","L0116440")
ClassMethod GetPatInfo(mi, labno) As %String
{
    s labno = $g(labno),mi=$g(mi)
    i $l(labno)=0 q ""
    s VisitNumberDR = $o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
    i '$l(VisitNumberDR) q ""
    //标本信息
    s TransmitDate=$tr($zd($h,3),"-")
    s RPVisitNumberData=$g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR))
    // IndexEpisodeNo On (TransmitDate, WorkGroupMachineDR, EpisodeNo)
    s MedicalRecordNo="",SpecimenDR="",Specimen="",EPIS=""
    s MedicalRecordNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,6)   //病案号
    s SpecimenDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,56)       //标本类型
    s EPIS=..GetEPIS(mi, labno)                  //鉴定号
    s AcceptDT=$p(EPIS,"^",2)
    s EPIS=$p(EPIS,"^",1) 
    i $l(SpecimenDR) s Specimen=$lg($g(^dbo.BTSpecimenD(SpecimenDR)),3)
    s LocationDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,22),Location=""
    i $l(LocationDR) s Location=$lg($g(^dbo.BTLocationD(LocationDR)),3)
    i Location["ICU" s Location="重症监护室"
    s DoctorDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,23),Doctor=""
    i $l(DoctorDR) s Doctor=$lg($g(^dbo.BTDoctorD(DoctorDR)),3)
    s ReceiveDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,66)
    s ReceiveTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,67)
    s ReceiveUserDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,68),ReceiveUser=""
    i $l(ReceiveUserDR) s ReceiveUser=$lg($g(^dbo.SYSUserD(ReceiveUserDR)),3)
    s RegNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,3)
    s SurName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,13)
    s GivenName=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,14)
    i SurName=GivenName s PatName=SurName
    e  s PatName=SurName_GivenName  
    s SpeciesDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,15),Species=""
    i $l(SpeciesDR) s Species=$lg($g(^dbo.BTSpeciesD(SpeciesDR)),3)
    s AdmTypeDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,4),AdmType=""
    i $l(AdmTypeDR) s AdmType=$lg($g(^dbo.BTAdmissionTypeD(AdmTypeDR)),3)
    s BedNo=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,27)
    s Age=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,18)
    s AgeUnitDR=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,19),AgeUnit=""
    i AgeUnitDR=1 s AgeUnit="y"
    i AgeUnitDR=2 s AgeUnit="m"
    i AgeUnitDR=3 s AgeUnit="d"
    i AgeUnitDR=4 s AgeUnit="h"
    //i $l(AgeUnitDR) s AgeUnit=$lg($g(^dbo.BTAgeUnitD(AgeUnitDR)),3)
    S Age=Age_AgeUnit
    s CollectDate=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,51)
    s CollectTime=$lg(RPVisitNumberData,52)
    s Diagnose=$tr($lg(RPVisitNumberData,28),",","，")
  
    s Sampleda=$zd($p($h,",",1),3)_" "_$zt($p($h,",",2))
    s Instrument = "XN"
    i $l(mi) s Instrument=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi),22)
    s Sampleno=labno   //检测号
    s Sampletype=""
    s Feetype="" ;费别
    s Srcdepno=Location  ;送检科室
    s Srcdocno=Doctor   ;送检医生
    s Userno=ReceiveUser ;检验医生(录入者)
    s Patno=RegNo ;登记号 ""
    s BarCode=""
    s Patna=PatName   ;病人姓名
    s Sex=1  ;性别
    i Species="男" s Sex="1"     ;1:男 ，2 女
    i Species ="女" s Sex="2"
    s Pattype=AdmType   ;病人类型
    s Bedno = BedNo    ;床号
    s Patage=Age  ;年龄
    s Ageunit=""   ;年龄单位
    s Reqno=labno  ;申请号 = 检验号
    s Reqda=""
    i $l(ReceiveDate) s Reqda=$e(ReceiveDate,1,4)_"-"_$e(ReceiveDate,5,6)_"-"_$e(ReceiveDate,7,8)_" "_$zt(ReceiveTime,2) ;送检日期 = 接收时间
    s Reportda=""   ;报告日期  = 初审(保存结果)时间
    s Printflag=""  ;打印标志
    s Resultflag=""  ;结果标志
    s Errflag=""  ;错误标志
    s Diagnose = Diagnose   ;诊断
    s Description=""  ;备注
    s Reserve=""  ;保留字段
    s Patnamn=""   ;姓名拼音码
    i $l(CollectDate) s Getda=$e(CollectDate,1,4)_"-"_$e(CollectDate,5,6)_"-"_$e(CollectDate,7,8)_" "_$zt(CollectTime,2) 
    e  s Getda=Reqda ;接收时间/采样日期
    s Wardno=""  ;病区
    s RetString=""
    s RetString=Sampleda_","_Instrument_","_Sampleno_","_Sampletype_","_Feetype_","_Srcdepno_","_Srcdocno_","_Userno_","
    s RetString=RetString_Patno_","_Patna_","_Sex_","_Pattype_","_Bedno_","_Patage_","_Ageunit_","_Reqno_","_Reqda_","
    s RetString=RetString_Reportda_","_Printflag_","_Resultflag_","_Errflag_","_Diagnose_","_Description_","_Reserve_","
    s RetString=RetString_Patnamn_","_Getda_","_Wardno_","_BarCode_","_MedicalRecordNo_","_Specimen_","_EPIS_","_AcceptDT
    q RetString
}

/// 监听做上传操作后调用改方法设置标本上传表状态
ClassMethod SaveSDFMTHD(mi, labno, epis, filename, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
    s mi=$g(mi),labno=$g(labno),epis = $g(epis),filename=$g(filename)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q
    s ret=##Class(MI.MachineUpload).SetSendFlag(mi,labno,"S",filename)
    q
}

}

/// 名称: MI.MIFCOBASE601
/// 描述: Cobas 6000 仪器接口  New Mode 
/// 通讯方式：双向
/// 编写者:liuzf
/// 编写日期: 20150827
/// 

MIFCOBASE601(MachID)  //仪器结果
   	s MachID=$g(MachID) 
	S ^TMPMACH10(MachID,104)=$H
	i '$l(MachID) q
	s ItemDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(MachID),12) //项目分隔符
	s ResultDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(MachID),13) //结果分隔符
	s AntDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(MachID),14) //抗生素分隔符
	s SenDeli=$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(MachID),15) //药敏结果分隔符
	s Port="|TCP|"_$li(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(MachID),10)  //端口号
	//控制字符
	s stx=$c(2),etx=$c(3),ack=$c(6),enq=$c(5),eot=$c(4),lf=$c(10),cr=$c(13),nak=$c(21),etb=$c(23)
	//s stx="[",etx="]"
	s AllRecord=""
	S ^TMPMACH10(MachID,102)=$H
	i $$Start^MI.MIF000(MachID) q
	f  d Main i $$Stop^MI.MIF000(MachID) q
  	c Port
  	q
  
Main 
  SET $ZTRAP="ERR"

  r *R:10 e  d  q
  .d ORDER
  i $c(R)=-1 w nak,*-3
  i $c(R)'=enq q
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,"ENQ","H<--M")
  d ACK
  f  r *R:10 q:$c(R)=eot  q:R=-1  d
  .i $c(R)'=stx q
  .s record=$$Read^MI.MIF000(MachID,"",lf) q:'$l(record)
  .d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,record,"H<--M")
  .d ACK
  .s record=$e(record,1,$l(record)-1)
  .i $l(record,etb)>1 s AllRecord=$g(AllRecord)_$p($e(record,2,$l(record)-1),etb,1)
  .i $l(record,etx)>1 s AllRecord=$g(AllRecord)_$p($e(record,2,$l(record)-1),etx,1)
  .d Result
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,$s($c(R)=eot:"EOT",1:R),"H<--M")
  d ORDER 
  q
  
Last	; file result if exist
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,epis_"$$"_result,"Result")
  i $l(epis),$l(result) d Save^MI.MIF000(MachID,epis,result,date,time,QC)
  s (epis,result,date,time,QC)=""
  q

Result
  //s num=$o(^TMP(mi,""),-1)+1
  //s ^TMP(mi,num)=AllRecord
  s headstr=""
  f k=1:1:$l(AllRecord,cr) d
  .s record=$p(AllRecord,cr,k)
  .i $e(record,1)="H" d  q
  ..s (sample,epis,surname,rec,res,result,date,time,QC)=""
  ..s headstr="1"_record
  .i $e(record,1)="Q" d  q
  ..;Q|1|^^              55163517^0^5066^1^^S1^SC||ALL||||||||A 
  ..S sampleID=$P($P(record,"|",3),"^",3)
  ..S sampleInfo=$P($P(record,"|",3),"^",4,9)
  ..S labno=$TR(sampleID," *")
  ..s rack=$tr($p($p(record,"|",3),"^",5)," ")
  ..s pos=$tr($p($p(record,"|",3),"^",6)," ") 
  ..;s retVal=$$ReceiveLabno^MI.MIF000(MachID,labno,rack_pos)
  ..;i retVal'=1 Quit
  ..i $l(labno) S ^TMP($zn,$j,"ENQ",labno)=sampleID_$C(2)_sampleInfo_$c(2)_rack_$c(2)_pos //
  .i $e(record,1)="O" d  q
  ..;-------双向取条码号---
  ..s epis=$tr($p($p(record,"|",3),"^",1)," ")
  ..i '$l(epis) s epis=$tr($p($p(record,"|",4),"^",1)," ")
  . ; result record
  .i $e(record,1)="R" d  q
  ..;R|1|^^^50/1/not|3.38|ng/ml||N||F|||||E11
  ..;R|2|^^^64//not|2.00|IU/L||LL||F|||||E22 
  ..s code=$p($p($p(record,"|",3),"^",4),"/",1)
  ..s res=$p(record,"|",4)
  ..i res["^" s res=$p(res,"^",2)
  ..s res=$tr(res," ")
  ..s Flag=$p(record,"|",7)
  ..i Flag="LL" s res="<"_res
  ..i Flag="HH" s res=">"_res
  ..i $l(code),$l(res) s result=result_code_ResultDeli_res_ItemDeli
  .; last record
  .i $e(record,1)="L" d Last
  i $l(AllRecord) s AllRecord=$p(AllRecord,cr,$l(AllRecord,cr))
  q

ORDER  ;ORDER LIST  ^TMP($zn,$j,"ENQ",epis
  i '$d(^TMP($zn)) q
  i '$d(^TMP($zn,$j)) q
  s labno="" f  s labno=$o(^TMP($zn,$j,"ENQ",labno)) q:labno=""  d
  .s requestData=^(labno)
  .s sampleID=$P(requestData,$C(2),1)
  .s sampleInfo=$P(requestData,$C(2),2)
  .s $p(headstr,"|",11)="TSDWN^REPLY"
  .s headstr=headstr_cr
  .//20140403 
  .s rackid=$p(requestData,$c(2),3)
  .s posid=$p(requestData,$c(2),4)
  .///保存位置号20110621 huhm
  .//d SetTSMachPos^MIF000(mi,labno,rackid,posid)
  .//  
  .d ScanOne^MI.MIF000(MachID,labno)  
  .s patstr=$$PATDET(labno)_cr
  .s tcx="",episx=labno
  .//s ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,MachID,labno,49)=""
  .//s ^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,MachID,labno,50)=""
  .s chl="" f  s chl=$o(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,MachID,labno,chl)) q:chl=""  d
  
  
  ..;i chl="148" d
  ...;s tcx=tcx_"^^^"_chl_"^20\"
  ..;e  s tcx=tcx_"^^^"_chl_"^\"
  
  ..s XSBS=$g(^TMP("MIFTESTCODE",$j,MachID,labno,chl))
  ..d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,chl_"项目稀释"_XSBS_"倍","稀释倍数")
  ..s tcx=tcx_"^^^"_chl_"^"_XSBS_"\"
  
  .s tcx=$e(tcx,1,$l(tcx)-1)
  .s SpecimenDR=""
  .s VisNumDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
  .i $l(VisNumDR) s SpecimenDR=$lg(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisNumDR),56)
  .S specimenTypeID="1",specimenType="血"
  .I $L(SpecimenDR) D
  ..S specimenType=$lg($g(^dbo.BTSpecimenD(SpecimenDR)),3) 
  .//标本类型代码,1=血清/血浆,2=尿,3=脑脊液,4=supmt,5=其他
  .S specimenID=$S(specimenType["血":1,specimenType["尿":2,specimenType["脑脊液":3,1:1)
  .///O|1|                CEA-10|0^5012^2^^S1^SC|^^^49^|R||||||N||||1|||||||20140324140016|||F
  .S ordstr="O|1|"_sampleID_"|"_sampleInfo_"|"
  .S ordstr=ordstr_tcx_"|R||"_$TR($ZD($P($H,",",1),3),"-")_$TR($ZT($P($H,",",2),1),":")_"||||N||||"_specimenID_"||||||||||O|||||"_cr
  .///L
  .s endstr="L|1|N"_cr
  .s str=headstr_patstr_ordstr_endstr
  .d Send(labno,str)   
  k ^TMP($zn,$j,"ENQ")
  q
  
PATDET(epis)  ; set patient details record
  s retstr="P|1"
  q retstr  
  
Send(epis,str)  ; send list of orders if exists
  w enq,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,"ENQ","H-->M")
  f j=1:1:10 r *R:1 i $c(R)=ack!($c(R)=enq) q
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,$s($c(R)=ack:"ACK",$c(R)=enq:"ENQ",$c(R)=nak:"NAK",1:R),"H<--M")
  i $c(R)=enq q
  i $c(R)'=ack w eot,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,"EOT","H-->M") q
  i $l(str)>241 d
  .s str1=$e(str,1,241)
  .s ret=$$SEND(str1,1)
  .s str2="2"_$e(str,242,$l(str))
  .s ret=$$SEND(str2,0)
  e  d
  .s ret=$$SEND(str,0)
  //f j=1:1:10 r *R:1 i $c(R)=ack!($c(R)=enq) q
  //d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,$s($c(R)=ack:"ACK",$c(R)=enq:"ENQ",$c(R)=nak:"NAK",1:R),"2H<--M")
  w eot,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,"EOT","H-->M") q
  h 0.2
  q
 
ERR
 h 10
 s ^TMPMachErr(+MachID,$j)=$ZERROR_".错误代码:"_$ECODE
 q 
  
SEND(str,flag)  ; send string to instrument
  i flag=1 d
  .s str=str_etb
  .s chsum=$$CHSUM(str)
  e  d
  .s str=str_etx
  .s chsum=$$CHSUM(str)
  w stx,str,chsum,cr,lf,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,str_chsum,"H-->M")
  f j=1:1:6 r *R:1 i ($c(R)=ack)!($c(R)=eot) q
  i $c(R)=ack d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,"ACK","H<--M") q 0
  i $c(R)=eot d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,"EOT","H<--M") q 0
  i $c(R)=-1 w nak,*-3
  d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,R,"H<--M")
  q 1

///w $$CHSUM^MI.MIFCOBASE601("3O^0101001N01300043225^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^M^^^20200115^1.021^59M^")
CHSUM(x)  ; calculate check sum
  n (x) s z=0 f y=1:1:$l(x) s z=z+$a(x,y)
  s z=$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#256\16+1)_$e("0123456789ABCDEF",z#16+1)
  q z
 ///发送回应符到仪器
ACK
  h 0.2
  s ack=$c(6)
  w ack,*-3 d Trace^MI.MIF000(MachID,"ACK","H-->M")
  q

	   
NEXTTRAY(tray)  
  q tray

item.title: 罗氏流水线IT3000
item.description:
接口说明

仪器厂商 罗氏流水线
 仪器型号 IT3000
通讯方式 主动上传
 仪器类型 生化发光流水线
医院名称 厦门翔安医院 程序名称 MI.MIFIT3000

仪器上接口标示和接口类型

  1. 接口类型：监听文件
  2. 连接方式：抓取RESULT结果文件和SEEN处理文件 .hl7文件，上传ORDERS .hl7文件

仪器接口说明

  • 罗氏流水线与lis交互分为处理文件 SEEN 和结果文件 RESULT 两种以及血清图片，处理文件过多，lis读取文件和解析文件同时进行，造成结果文件无法及时解析，造成仪器传了结果但是未及时读取造成无法及时发报告。针对这一问题，详细在问题处理中无法及时读取文件处理造成获取结果过慢记录。
  • 接口中包含多种功能，包含血清图片，自动核收，报警信息存储等。详细在仪器个性功能中展示。

 	s commandchild="" //前处理命令初始化
 	s DealDateStr="" //MSH 时间初始化
 	s (sample,result,date,time,QC)=""
 	//解析多行合并数据
 	f i=1:1:$l(recordbak,"[13][10]"){
	 	s record=$p(recordbak,"[13][10]",i)
	 	;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"解析行数据")
	 	i '$l(record) q
	 	s type=$p(record,"|",1)	//取出消息头命令类型
		//解析MSH命令
		i type="MSH"{
		 	s DateStr=$p(record,"|",7)	//取日期串
		 	i $l(DateStr)=14 s DealDateStr=$e(DateStr,1,8)_","_(($e(DateStr,9,10)*3600)+($e(DateStr,11,12)*60))	//解析保存日期串
	 	}
	 	//解析EQU命令	包含前处理后处理指令，根据指令记录对应事件
	 	i type="EQU"{
		 	//前处理名称	RSA1 流水线处理信息，e801、P501_701	仪器处理信息
		 	s commandName=$p($p(record,"|",3),"^",4)
		 	//获取前处理命令，SEEN 上机事件，RESULT 前处理分区事件，RSA1 未知事件，ARCHIVE 归档事件
		 	s commandchild=$p($p(record,"|",3),"^",7)
		 	;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,commandchild,"前处理命令")
	 	}
	 	//解析SAC命令	根据EQU命令重获取到的前处理事件，进行LIS相关处理
	 	//本接口包括 SEEN 自动核收，ARCHIVE 记录归档位置
	 	i type="SAC"{
		 	s epis=$p(record,"|",5)	//取出流水号
		 	s machCode=$p(record,"|",11)	//取出前处理分区信息或仪器信息
		 	s positioninfo=$p(record,"|",12)	//取出位置信息
		 	//前处理SEEN 自动核收
		 	i commandchild="SEEN"{
			 	;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"分区信息，标本号:"_epis_"的样本所在分区:"_machCode_" "_positioninfo,"H<--M")
			 	i commandName="RSA1" j ..SaveRecord(epis,"分区位置:"_machCode_"-"_positioninfo,mi,"100")	//前处理分区
			 	e  j ..SaveRecord(epis,"上机位置:"_commandName_"-"_positioninfo,mi,"6")	//上机
			 	try{d ..ZDHS(mi,epis,machCode,positioninfo)}catch ex{d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,ex.Data,"自动核收提示")}		//自动核收
			 	i commandName="RSA1" d
			 	.i (","_..#FQCode_",")'[(","_machCode_",") d	//$TS$ 只有流水线仪器记录分区架子号
			 	..j ..SaveRackNo(epis,machCode_"-"_positioninfo,mi,"分区")
			 	e  j ..SaveRackNo(epis,commandName_"-"_positioninfo,mi,"上机")
		 	}
		 	//前处理RESULT 处理分区信息
		 	i commandchild="RESULT"{
			 	s curMachName=machCode	//通过仪器对照码取仪器
			 	//此处存标本全部分区预处理的位置号	针对非流水线标本分拣
			 	i commandName="RSA1" j ..SaveRecord(epis,"分区位置:"_positioninfo,mi,"100")	//前处理分区
			 	i commandName="RSA1" j ..SaveRackNo(epis,positioninfo,mi,"分区")
		 	}
		 	//前处理ARCHIVE 处理归档信息
		 	i commandchild="ARCHIVE"{
			 	s curMachName=machCode	//通过仪器对照码取仪器
			 	//此处存标本全部审核报告的位置号
			 	;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"归档信息，标本号:"_epis_"的样本所在仪器:"_curMachName_" "_positioninfo,"H<--M")
			 	;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"执行记录分类信息:"_positioninfo,"H<--M")
			 	i commandName="RSA1" d
			 	.j ..SaveRackNo(epis,positioninfo,mi,"归档")	//保存归档信息到架子号
			 	.j ..SaveRecord(epis,"冰箱归档位置:"_positioninfo,mi,"62")	//冰箱归档
			 	e  d
			 	.j ..SaveRackNo(epis,positioninfo,mi,"归档中")	//保存归档信息到架子号
			 	.j ..SaveRecord(epis,"归档中位置:"_positioninfo,mi,"62")	//归档
			 	;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"记录归档信息完成","H<--M")
			 
			 
		 	}
	 	}
	 
	 	//解析质控数据,P业务数据，Q质控数据
	 	i type="ORC"{
		 	s epis=$p(record,"|",3)
	 	}
	 
	 	i type="OBR"{
		 	s epis=$p(record,"|",3)
	 	}
	 	//仪器报警信息
	 	i type="NTE"{
		 	s WaringStr=$p(record,"|",4)
		 	s WaringCode=$p(WaringStr," ",2)
		 	;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"仪器报警信息:"_WaringStr,"H<--M")
		 	//保存仪器报警信息到组内报告评价
		 	;d ..SaveResultWarned(epis,WaringStr,mi)
	 	}
	 	try{j ##class(MI.Special.Record).RecordData(epis,recordbak,"LSLSXGET",1,1,10)}catch{}	//YHR 20230828 记录十天的数据
	 	i type="OBX"{
		 	s machCode=$p(record,"|",16)	//仪器信息和架子号信息
		 	s code=$p($p(record,"|",4),"^",1)
		 	s res=$p(record,"|",6)
		 	s CallThePolice=$p(record,"|",9)	//项目报警信息
		 	s res=..ConvertResult(code,res)		//结果特殊转换
		 	i $l(CallThePolice) d
		 	.s result=result_code_$c(92)_res_$c(92)_$c(92)_CallThePolice_$c(44)		//YHR 20250328 将报警信息存入到其他结果字段
		 	.try{j ..SaveResultWarned(epis,"存在仪器报警信息",mi,"41")}catch{}		//YHR 20250329 存储报警信息标志，此处41为常规生化工作小组$TS$
		 	e  s result=result_code_$c(92)_res_$c(44)
	 	}
 	}
 	i $l(result) d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"H<--M")
 	//统一保存结果
 	i $l(epis),$l(result){
	 	i $l(DealDateStr){	//如果记录到时间，则根据仪器时间存储结果。
	 		s date=$p(DealDateStr,",",1)
	 		s time=$p(DealDateStr,",",2)
	 		i $l(date)'=8 s date="",time=""
	 	
	 	}
	 	d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Save(mi, epis, result, date, time, QC)
 	}
		 
	q ""
}

/// 结果特殊转换
/// $TS$
/// W ##CLASS(MI.MIFIT3000N1).ConvertResult("9PA","<0.070")
ClassMethod ConvertResult(code, res)
{
	i code="9PA" d
	.i $e(res)="<",+$e(res,2,*)=".07" d
	..s res="<70"
	q res
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }
    Else      { 
        Set Row=^CacheTemp(repid,ind)
    }
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

/********************************************自动核收开始****************************************************/
/// 仪器主键，条码号，前处理标本分区标识，仪器信息(位置)
/// w ##class(MI.MIFIT3000N1).ZDHS("34","8000000352","WANTAI")
/// w ##class(MI.MIFIT300N).ZDHS("34","1003779663","RSA1")
ClassMethod ZDHS(mi, Labno, MachineCode, positioninfo)
{
 	s mi=$g(mi),Labno=$g(Labno),machCode=$g(MachineCode),positioninfo=$g(positioninfo)
 	i '$l(Labno) q ""
 	/*---------->判断该标本是否已接收未核收 开始<----------*/
 	s QuitFlag=0
 	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Labno))) d
 	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Labno),""))
 	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR)) s QuitFlag=1
 	i QuitFlag=1 q ""
 	/*---------->判断该标本是否已接收未核收 结束<----------*/
 	s curWorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)	//得到当前仪器关联工作小组信息
 	s CurWorkGroupDR=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(curWorkGroupMachineDR),4)
 	s curMachName=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),5)
 	s AcceptFlag=$lg($g(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(curWorkGroupMachineDR)),13)	//得到仪器工作小组的核收类型
 
 	//AcceptFlag为1认为是前处理工作小组，如果是前处理小组，就认为上前处理	本接口未设置前处理工作小组，未对此流程进行测试
 	i AcceptFlag="1"  d QCLZDHS
 	e  d ZDHS
 	q ""
 
ZDHS
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"上仪器,标本号:"_Labno_"的标本在:"_curMachName_",分区位置:"_MachineCode_",样本所在:"_positioninfo,"自动核收")

	//根据前处理标本分区进行分区自动核收，并且根据分区代码是否核收进行区分
	//本接口认为 默认认为罗氏流水线核收，如果分区代码中包含 【BHS】则认为标本不核收，此块代码将仪器传过来的分区代码进行归类
	//本接口关联标本分区， WANTAI 万泰-->W，XINCHANYE 新产业-->X，LINJIAN 临检凝血-->L，XIEGUANG 携光-->R，罗氏-->Y，不核收-->N
 	s HsFlag="Y",WorkGroupMachineDR=""
 	i (MachineCode["WANTAI")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"WANTAI","")
 	.s HsFlag="W"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=48	//未核收且分区是WANTAI
 	i (MachineCode["XINCHANYE")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"XINCHANYE","")
 	.s HsFlag="X"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=50	//未核收且分区是XINCHANYE
 	i (MachineCode["LINJIAN")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"LINJIAN","")
 	.s HsFlag="L"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=9		//未核收且分区是LINJIAN
 	i (MachineCode["XIEGUANG")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"XIEGUANG","")
 	.s HsFlag="R"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=67	//未核收且分区是XIEGUANG
 	i (MachineCode["BHS_") d	;BHS_WANTAI
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"BHS_","")
 	.s HsFlag="N"
 	i MachineCode="C_C8K886" s MachineCode="C801"
 	i MachineCode="C_C8K77" s MachineCode="C701"
 	i MachineCode="C8K886" s MachineCode="C801"
 	i MachineCode="C8K77" s MachineCode="C701"
 	i HsFlag="Y" d
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=41	//未核收且分区不包含BHS_	默认核收到罗氏流水线
 	i '$l(WorkGroupMachineDR) q
 	s ret=..ReceiveLabNoByWGM(WorkGroupMachineDR,Labno,$zd(+$h,8))
 	s WorkGroupDR=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),4)
 	i ret'="1" d
 	.s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    .s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR		//自动核收出错显示再对应的工作组
    .s SendRet=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收失败"", ""info"": """_Labno_"前处理核收失败:"_ret_",仪器【"_curMachName_"】！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
 	j ..SaveRecord(Labno,"自动核收:"_ret,"","14",WorkGroupMachineDR)
	q ret

QCLZDHS
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"上前处理，鉴定号:"_Labno_"的标本在:"_curMachName_",样本所在:"_positioninfo,"DealInfo")
 	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"执行核收到前处理","DealInfo")
 	//此处核收医嘱导前处理工作小组，不生成项目，写标本操作日志
 	s dealret=##Class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).PreDealLabNo(mi,Labno,"") 
 	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,Labno_"核收到前处理返回信息:"_dealret,"DealInfo")
 	//记录位置信息到报告位置号
 	d ..SaveRackNo(Labno,positioninfo,mi)
 	i dealret["标本已核收" q 
 	i dealret="1" d
 	.//写标本操作日志
 	.d ..SaveRecord(Labno,machCode,mi,"5")
 	e  d
 	.s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    .s perUser = "WG-"_CurWorkGroupDR
    .s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收失败"", ""info"": """_Labno_"前处理核收失败:"_dealret_",仪器【"_curMachName_"】！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
 	.//写标本操作日志
 	.d ..SaveRecord(Labno,dealret,mi,"100")
 	q
}

/// Others  w ##Class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).ReceiveLabNoByWGM("3","1000004476","20191105") 
/// 按工作小组核收医嘱
/// INPUT: MachID:仪器主键，LabNo：条码号，TransmitDate：上机日期（不传默认当天）
/// OutPut: RetValue:1成功
ClassMethod ReceiveLabNoByWGM(WorkGroupMachineDR As %String, LabNo As %String, TransmitDate, RackNo, RuleCode) As %String
{
	s WorkGroupMachineDR=$g(WorkGroupMachineDR)
	s LabNo=$g(LabNo)
	s TransmitDate=$g(TransmitDate)
	s RuleCode=$g(RuleCode)
	s RackNo=$g(RackNo)
	s NowDate=$zd($h,8)
	s RetValue=1
	i '$l(TransmitDate) s TransmitDate=NowDate
	i '$l(WorkGroupMachineDR) q 100

	s WorkGroupMachineCode=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),2)

	s WorkGroupMachineName=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),3)
	s WorkGroupDR=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),4)
	s DepartmentDR=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupD(WorkGroupDR),4)
    s HospitalDR=$lg(^dbo.BTDepartmentD(DepartmentDR),4)
    s WorkGroupMachineDesc=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),3)
    s IndexOperateType=##class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData("H")
    s AutoDR=$O(^dbo.RPWGMachineAutoI("IndexOperateType",IndexOperateType,WorkGroupMachineDR,""))

    }
  
    s MachineAutoData=$g(^dbo.RPWGMachineAutoD(AutoDR))
  
    s IsOpen=$LG(MachineAutoData,4)
    i IsOpen'=1 
    {
	    s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    	s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR
    	s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""未开启自动核收"", ""info"": """_"工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineName_"】未开启自动核收！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
	    q "-1^该工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineDesc_"】未开启自动核收！"
    }
    s CurrentDate = $p($h,",",1)
	s Currenttime = $p($h,",",2)

	//开始时间
	s StartDate=$lg(MachineAutoData,5)
	i $l(StartDate) s StartDate= $zdh(StartDate,8)
	s StartTime=$lg(MachineAutoData,6)
	//结束时间
	s EndDate=$lg(MachineAutoData,7)
	i $l(EndDate) s EndDate= $zdh(EndDate,8)
	s EndTime=$lg(MachineAutoData,8)
	//时间类型
	s TimeType=$lg(MachineAutoData,9)
	i TimeType="CT"  //连续
    {
	    i (CurrentDate<StartDate)||(($l(StartTime))&&(CurrentDate=StartDate)&&(Currenttime<StartTime)) 
	    {
		    s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    		s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR
    		s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收日期未生效"", ""info"": """_"工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineName_"】自动核收日期未生效！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
		    q "-1^该工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineDesc_"】自动核收日期未生效！"
	    }
	    i (CurrentDate>EndDate)||(($l(EndTime))&&(CurrentDate=EndDate)&&(Currenttime>EndTime) ) 
	    {
		    s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    		s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR
    		s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收日期已失效"", ""info"": """_"工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineName_"】自动核收日期已失效！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
		    q "-1^该工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineDesc_"】自动核收日期已失效！"
	    }
	}
	i TimeType="TS"  //时间段
	{
		i (CurrentDate<StartDate)||(($l(StartTime))&&(Currenttime<StartTime))
		{
			s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    		s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR
    		s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收日期未生效"", ""info"": """_"工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineName_"】自动核收日期未生效！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
			q "-1^该工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineDesc_"】自动核收日期未生效！"
		}
	    i (CurrentDate>EndDate)||(($l(EndTime))&&(Currenttime>EndTime))
	    {
		    s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    		s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR
    		s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收日期已失效"", ""info"": """_"工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineName_"】自动核收日期已失效！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
			q "-1^该工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineDesc_"】自动核收日期已失效！"  
		}
	}
  
    s AcceptUserDR="" i $l(AutoDR) s AcceptUserDR=$LG($g(^dbo.RPWGMachineAutoD(AutoDR)),10)
    i '$l(AcceptUserDR) d
    .s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    .s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR
    .s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""未设置负责人"", ""info"": """_"工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineName_"】未设置核收负责人！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
    i '$l(AcceptUserDR) q "-1^该工作小组【"_WorkGroupMachineDesc_"】未设置核收负责人！"
    s CommDirection=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),11)
	///判断医嘱是否核收
	S AcceptFlag=0
	s IsSpecialFlag=0
	s CheckItemList=""
	s PreReportDR=""
	k TestSetList
	s LabNoType=##Class(LISSP.DHCRPVisitNumber).GetLabNoType(LabNo)
	s WebNamespace=##Class(OTH.SYSParameter).GetWebNamespace()
    i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(LabNo))){
	     
           s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(LabNo),""))
           S TestSetDR=""
           f {
	          s TestSetDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberTestSetI("IndexMaster",VisitNumberDR,TestSetDR))
	          q:TestSetDR=""
	          s RowID=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberTestSetI("IndexMaster",VisitNumberDR,TestSetDR,""))
              i $l(RowID){
	             s TestSetGroup="Default" //工作小组下分组类型
                 s WGMDR=$LG($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberTestSetD(RowID)),5)
                 i '$l(WGMDR) s CheckItemList=TestSetDR_CheckItemList
                 S AccpetReportDR=$LG($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberTestSetD(RowID)),11)
                 I $L(AccpetReportDR) s AccpetWGMDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(AccpetReportDR)),4) I $LG($g(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(AccpetWGMDR)),13)'=1 continue
                 s AcceptFlag=0
                 I $L(WGMDR) S AcceptFlag=$LG($g(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WGMDR)),13) //是否是前处理小组
                 I AcceptFlag=1 S PreReportDR= $LG($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberTestSetD(RowID)),11),IsSpecialFlag=1
                 I AcceptFlag=1,$D(^dbo.BTTestSetWorkGroupMachineI("IndexMaster",TestSetDR,WorkGroupMachineDR))
                 {
	                  //处理报告分组信息
	                  i $d(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineRuleTSI("IndexTestSet",TestSetDR))
	                  {
		                   s WorkGroupMachineRuleDR=""
		                   f{
			                   s WorkGroupMachineRuleDR=$o(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineRuleTSI("IndexTestSet",TestSetDR,WorkGroupMachineRuleDR)) 
			                   q:WorkGroupMachineRuleDR=""
			                   s GroupWGMDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineRuleD(WorkGroupMachineRuleDR)),4)
			                   s IsShow=$lg($g(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineRuleD(WorkGroupMachineRuleDR)),5)
			                   i WorkGroupMachineDR'=GroupWGMDR continue
			                   i IsShow="1" continue
			                   s TestSetGroup=WorkGroupMachineRuleDR
			                }  
		              }
		              s TestSetList(TestSetGroup,TestSetDR)=""

              }

    }
    s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(LabNo),""))
    //前处理标本核收
    i IsSpecialFlag=1
    {

	    s maxEpis=..GetMaxMiEpisodeNo(WorkGroupMachineDR,TransmitDate)
        Set $ZTrap = "ErrorHandle"

        s MajorConclusion="",OldEpi="",MiniConclusion=""
        i $l(PreReportDR) s MajorConclusion=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(PreReportDR)),40),MiniConclusion=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(PreReportDR)),41),OldEpi=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(PreReportDR)),8)
        s maxEpis=OldEpi
        s TestSetGroup=""
        f{
	        s TestSetGroup=$o(TestSetList(TestSetGroup))
	        q:TestSetGroup=""  
	        s objVisitNumberReport=##class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReport).%New()
			s objVisitNumberReport.VisitNumberDR=VisitNumberDR
			s objVisitNumberReport.TransmitDate=TransmitDate
			s objVisitNumberReport.WorkGroupMachineDR=WorkGroupMachineDR

			  s OrderNo=(OrderNo +1)
		    }
		    s AssayNo=""

	        i '$l(AssayNo) s AssayNo=maxEpis
			s objVisitNumberReport.AccessionNo=""   ///细菌分离号

			s objVisitNumberReport.EpisodeNo=maxEpis
			i $l(maxEpis) s ^DHCLABWGMEPSIDERECORD("WGM",WorkGroupMachineDR,TransmitDate,maxEpis)=""

		    I '$D(TestSetList(TestSetGroup)) s RetValue="-1^无可核收医嘱"   q

        i $l(PreReportDR),'$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberTestSetI("IndexReportID",PreReportDR)){

                 If ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)){s RetValue="删除报告信息失败:"_$SYSTEM.Status.GetErrorText(sc)    }
	    }
	    i RetValue'=1 TROLLBACK  Quit RetValue 
	    TCOMMIT
	    i $l(WorkGroupMachineDR),$l(maxEpis) s ret=##Class(HIS.DHCCommon).SaveWorkGroupMachineEpis(WorkGroupMachineDR,TransmitDate,maxEpis,"")
	  
	}
	else
	{

		s Param=Param_"<P3>"_maxEpis_"</P3>"
		s Param=Param_"<P4>"_AcceptUserDR_"</P4><P5></P5><P6></P6><P7></P7>"
		s Param=Param_"<P8>"_WorkGroupMachineDR_"</P8><P9></P9><P10></P10><P11></P11><P12>"_RackNo_"</P12><P13></P13><P14>@@1@@"_Flag_"</P14></Data>"
		s Sessions=AcceptUserDR_"^"_WorkGroupDR_"^^^"_HospitalDR
		b ;a KSZDHS
		s ret=##Class(LISSP.DHCRPVisitNumber).ReceiveVisitNumber(LabNo,Param,Sessions)
		i $p(ret,"^",1)'="1" s RetValue=ret
    } 
	q RetValue

ErrorHandle
	TROLLBACK
	s RetValue="-1^错误"_$tr($ZERROR,"^","--")_".错误代码:"_$ECODE
    Quit RetValue
}

/// Creator：      YHR

/// Description：  通过编号规则获取工作小组最大流水号

/// Others		   【原】w ##Class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).GetMaxMiEpisodeNo("41","20250319")
/// k ^TMP("MI.MIFIT3000N1.1","WGMEpis","41")
/// w ##Class(MI.MIFIT3000N1).GetMaxMiEpisodeNo("41","20250319")
ClassMethod GetMaxMiEpisodeNo(WorkGroupMachineDR As %String, TransmitDate As %String) As %String
{
	S TransmitDate=$g(TransmitDate)

	S RetValue=""
	i '$l(WorkGroupMachineDR) q RetValue
	i '$l(TransmitDate) s TransmitDate=$zd($h,8)

	//记录该工作小组当天最大的流水号，如果有记录，则优先判断是否核收成功，如果未核收成功仍旧使用该号码
	i $d(^TMP($zn,"WGMEpis",WorkGroupMachineDR,TransmitDate)) d
	.s JLEpis=$g(^TMP($zn,"WGMEpis",WorkGroupMachineDR,TransmitDate))

	i $l(RetValue) s ^TMP($zn,"WGMEpis",WorkGroupMachineDR,TransmitDate)=RetValue q RetValue

	s Parameter="<Data><P3></P3><P12></P12><P4></P4><P0>"_TransmitDate_"</P0><P8></P8><P10></P10><P5></P5><P1></P1><P13></P13><P9></P9><P14></P14><P6></P6><P2></P2><P11></P11><P7></P7></Data>"

	i $l(WGMEpisNo) s RetValue=WGMEpisNo
	q RetValue

通过编号规则获取自动核收对应的流水号

本方法通过维护编号规则，编号规则代码与工作小组代码相同时，从编号规则获取对应工作小组流水号。

避免核收失败流水号浪费造成跳号情况，本方法做出以下处理。

1.先进行判断编号规则当前号是否在对应工作小组有报告，如果没有的话则还使用当前的流水号再次进行核收，如果有的话，则进入到下一个获取流水号的逻辑。

2.通过编号规则获取下一个流水号，并进行最大1000次的判断循环取号，避免号重复核收失败。

3.如果未通过编号规则获取到流水号，获取失败或者没有维护对应的编号规则，则获取当前工作小组最大流水号

{
	S TransmitDate=$g(TransmitDate)

	S RetValue=""
	i '$l(WorkGroupMachineDR) q RetValue

	i $d(^dbo.SYSRuleNoBaseI("IndexCode",WorkGroupMachineCode)) d
	.s RuleNoBasDR=$o(^dbo.SYSRuleNoBaseI("IndexCode",WorkGroupMachineCode,""))
	.s JLEpis=$lg($g(^dbo.SYSRuleNoBaseD(RuleNoBasDR)),5)
	.i '$l(JLEpis) q

	s WGMEpisNo=##Class(LISSP.DHCRPVisitNumberReport).GetMaxEpisodeNo(WorkGroupMachineDR,Parameter) 			//YHR 20250317 获取最大流水号报错问题处理

特殊处理记录

本节点为该仪器接口特殊处理的部分，可以参考实际修改使用

监听配置，有多条监听配置

主监听配置会获取仪器主键，其他的无法获取只能写死，主键有根据项目实际情况修改

自动核收调用核收方法，按照工作小组主键入参。

自动核收前处理

由于自动核收功能包括罗氏本流水线自动核收，同时还带有分拣功能，对于免疫标本和临检标本分区和自动核收。本部分为特殊处理部分。

本部分分为两块，一块为接收时上传维护，此部分与科室进行核对维护，另一部分为接收分区标识，根据仪器分区进行核收。（注：未通过检验自己维护的项目分区进行核收，一部分是减少调用增加处理速度，另一部分是根据仪器分区，方便科室对应分区找到对应工作小组的标本。）

1.生化的标本都会立马拔盖上机去做，对于其他的标本，比如免疫和临检的标本，涉及到是否拔盖和分区的逻辑。仪器分别该标本类型，则需要通过检验上传对应条码的相关信息，因此，在流水线工作组中，对应医嘱维护不同的检测项目，在接收的时候就会获取流水线的医嘱对应的项目，在上传通道号维护对应的标识。

2.标本上机仪器回传分区标识进行自动核收

优先判断是否已接收未核收，如果已经核收则直接退出。

根据前处理标本分区标识进行自动核收（此标识跟仪器进行核对不同的分区标识），通过不同的标识获取对应的工作小组，或者BHS_标识只记录分区不进行核收。核收失败进行弹窗提示。

/// 仪器主键，条码号，前处理标本分区标识，仪器信息(位置)
/// w ##class(MI.MIFIT3000N1).ZDHS("34","8000000352","WANTAI")
/// w ##class(MI.MIFIT300N).ZDHS("34","1003779663","RSA1")
ClassMethod ZDHS(mi, Labno, MachineCode, positioninfo)
{
 	s mi=$g(mi),Labno=$g(Labno),machCode=$g(MachineCode),positioninfo=$g(positioninfo)
 	i '$l(Labno) q ""
 	/*---------->判断该标本是否已接收未核收 开始<----------*/
 	s QuitFlag=0
 	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Labno))) d
 	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Labno),""))
 	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR)) s QuitFlag=1
 	i QuitFlag=1 q ""
 	/*---------->判断该标本是否已接收未核收 结束<----------*/
 	s curWorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)	//得到当前仪器关联工作小组信息
 	s CurWorkGroupDR=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(curWorkGroupMachineDR),4)
 	s curMachName=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),5)
 	s AcceptFlag=$lg($g(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(curWorkGroupMachineDR)),13)	//得到仪器工作小组的核收类型
 
 	//AcceptFlag为1认为是前处理工作小组，如果是前处理小组，就认为上前处理	本接口未设置前处理工作小组，未对此流程进行测试
 	i AcceptFlag="1"  d QCLZDHS
 	e  d ZDHS
 	q ""
 
ZDHS
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"上仪器,标本号:"_Labno_"的标本在:"_curMachName_",分区位置:"_MachineCode_",样本所在:"_positioninfo,"自动核收")

	//根据前处理标本分区进行分区自动核收，并且根据分区代码是否核收进行区分
	//本接口认为 默认认为罗氏流水线核收，如果分区代码中包含 【BHS】则认为标本不核收，此块代码将仪器传过来的分区代码进行归类
	//本接口关联标本分区， WANTAI 万泰-->W，XINCHANYE 新产业-->X，LINJIAN 临检凝血-->L，XIEGUANG 携光-->R，罗氏-->Y，不核收-->N
 	s HsFlag="Y",WorkGroupMachineDR=""
 	i (MachineCode["WANTAI")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"WANTAI","")
 	.s HsFlag="W"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=48	//未核收且分区是WANTAI
 	i (MachineCode["XINCHANYE")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"XINCHANYE","")
 	.s HsFlag="X"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=50	//未核收且分区是XINCHANYE
 	i (MachineCode["LINJIAN")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"LINJIAN","")
 	.s HsFlag="L"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=9		//未核收且分区是LINJIAN
 	i (MachineCode["XIEGUANG")&&(MachineCode'["BHS") d
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"XIEGUANG","")
 	.s HsFlag="R"
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=67	//未核收且分区是XIEGUANG
 	i (MachineCode["BHS_") d	;BHS_WANTAI
 	.S MachineCode=$REPLACE(MachineCode,"BHS_","")
 	.s HsFlag="N"
 	i MachineCode="C_C8K886" s MachineCode="C801"
 	i MachineCode="C_C8K77" s MachineCode="C701"
 	i MachineCode="C8K886" s MachineCode="C801"
 	i MachineCode="C8K77" s MachineCode="C701"
 	i HsFlag="Y" d
 	.s WorkGroupMachineDR=41	//未核收且分区不包含BHS_	默认核收到罗氏流水线
 	i '$l(WorkGroupMachineDR) q
 	s ret=..ReceiveLabNoByWGM(WorkGroupMachineDR,Labno,$zd(+$h,8))
 	s WorkGroupDR=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),4)
 	i ret'="1" d
 	.s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    .s perUser = "WG-"_WorkGroupDR		//自动核收出错显示再对应的工作组
    .s SendRet=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收失败"", ""info"": """_Labno_"前处理核收失败:"_ret_",仪器【"_curMachName_"】！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
 	j ..SaveRecord(Labno,"自动核收:"_ret,"","14",WorkGroupMachineDR)
	q ret

QCLZDHS
	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"上前处理，鉴定号:"_Labno_"的标本在:"_curMachName_",样本所在:"_positioninfo,"DealInfo")
 	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"执行核收到前处理","DealInfo")
 	//此处核收医嘱导前处理工作小组，不生成项目，写标本操作日志
 	s dealret=##Class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).PreDealLabNo(mi,Labno,"") 
 	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,Labno_"核收到前处理返回信息:"_dealret,"DealInfo")
 	//记录位置信息到报告位置号
 	d ..SaveRackNo(Labno,positioninfo,mi)
 	i dealret["标本已核收" q 
 	i dealret="1" d
 	.//写标本操作日志
 	.d ..SaveRecord(Labno,machCode,mi,"5")
 	e  d
 	.s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    .s perUser = "WG-"_CurWorkGroupDR
    .s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": ""自动核收失败"", ""info"": """_Labno_"前处理核收失败:"_dealret_",仪器【"_curMachName_"】！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
 	.//写标本操作日志
 	.d ..SaveRecord(Labno,dealret,mi,"100")
 	q
}

/// Query的执行方法
/// d ##class(%ResultSet).RunQuery("MI.MIFIT3000N1","QryLabInfo","34","","","","","","","","","","","","","","","")
ClassMethod QryLabInfoExecute(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, mi As %String, P1, P2, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %Status
{
    Set repid=$i(^CacheTemp)

    s LabnoList=""

    //*-------------------------------->*申请项目
    s AddDate=$zd($p($h,",",1)-1,8) f  s AddDate=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData("C"),AddDate)) q:(AddDate="")||(OutPutNum>6)  d

    ..s OutPutNum=OutPutNum+1

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }
    Else      { 
        Set Row=^CacheTemp(repid,ind)
    }
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

问题处理记录

本节点为接口使用过程中踩过的雷和遇到过的问题以及处理方案

无法及时读取文件处理造成获取结果过慢

1.修改监听配置，允许同一台电脑上存在多个监听。（新版本监听支持，本接口对应使用软件在附件中）

监听中存在两个配置，AllowMultiOpen（是否允许多开，1允许，0不允许，默认不允许） 和OpenMessageService（多开版本维护为0，如果是1的话会造成系统崩溃！！！如果是正常在用电脑，其中一个维护为1就可以，其他的一定要设置为0）

在监听配置中，配置多个监听读取。本接口配置多个监听，主监听读取结果，额外配置两个，一个读取流水线处理文件，一个读取图片和上传信息（！！！这两个功能一定要在一起，上传参数 "UPPreDealClass":"PreDeal.DealDemoM,PreDeal" 配置后，就一定会主动上传文件，所以一定一定一定再一起！！！）

2.使用job线程处理。监听固定调用对应接口的fileMTHD方法，读取结果与系统其他方法没有交互，因此将具体的处理方法另外写了方法 ResultDo ，通过文件名包含路径进行判断，如果是结果RESULT文件，用job调用存储结果，如果是处理SEEN文件，用do调用处理结果。加快解析读取结果速度。

仪器未获取到项目问题

1.读取结果不能及时时，进行了监听配置配置多个监听，最开始是为了分工明确，设置了四个监听，一个用来读取结果RESULT，一个用来读取处理文件SEEN，一个用来上传信息，一个用来读取图片。读取图片的配置和上传信息的配置处理类是同一个，读取图片多了一个额外的读取图片路径。

最开始认为，读取图片的配置，不配置上传信息的路径，就不会进行上传。后面科室经常说会有漏标本漏项目的情况，经过多次排查核对日志后，发现被读取图片配置的监听上传了文件，因为没有配置上传路径，将上传的文件存在了监听对应的根路径。后面修改为上传信息和读取图片合为一个监听，最终为三个监听，一个读取结果，一个读取处理文件，一个上传信息+读取图片。

2.修改后仍旧有漏项目的情况，确定仪器电脑只有三个监听，三个监听的日志都有认真排查。后面使用获取调用webservice的ip方法 w ##Class(LIS.Util.Common).GetClientIP()，查询到有其他电脑配置了监听，造成被其他电脑抢走了。

3.上传过快造成未接收完标本已经上传，造成漏项目问题，判断接收5s内不上传。遇到偶发问题，上传时间与接收时间为0甚至上传时间比接收时间早1s，判断是事务未完成已经发送。设置上传时间大于-2秒不上传。

报警信息过长保存到其他结果字段时造成无法保存仪器结果

报警信息存放在结果说明字段，会将结果说明字段发送给临床医生，很多医院要求报警信息不发送给临床医生，因此将报警信息存放至其他结果字段。然而其他结果字段，在dbo.RPMachineResult仪器结果表和dbo.RPMachineResultLog仪器结果日志表中字段OtherRes设置长度较短，就会造成存储时报错但是前台没有任何提示。扩长后可以正常的对应到结果。

如果仪器维护报警结果不传输，如果没有结果，其他结果也不会赋值，因此要根据实际进行判断，如果有报警信息但是没有结果，设置结果为ERR，报警信息就可以正常的保存显示。

同时存在大量标本，查询速度过慢，造成堆积无法正常上传项目

批量手工登记，造成同时存在超多标本等待上传，由于主动上传查询query中，包含申请项目上传，复查项目上传，回退项目上传和审核项目上传，造成查询速度过慢

监听查询等待时间为60s，如果超过时间认为查询超时，就不再等待进行上传，会提示查询错误超过50次。因此对于接口进行处理，申请项目上传分批上传，超过10个就停止查询直接输出。

‍

ClassMethod fileMTHD(mi, record, epis, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
	s mi=$g(mi)
	s epis=$g(epis)
  	i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q "0"
  	s HospitalDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),4)
	i '$l(record) q "0"
	i '$d(^TMPLIS("RS600",mi,"ERR")) s ^TMPLIS("RS600",mi,"ERR")=""
 	d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,record,"H<--M")
 	s miold=mi
 	s recordbak=record
 	//仪器临时结果映射
 	s TMPMachResMap=""
 	//解析多行合并数据
 	f i=1:1:$l(recordbak,"#enter#") d
 	.s record=$p(recordbak,"#enter#",i)
 	.d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"解析行数据:"_record,"H<--M")
 	.i '$l(record) q
 	.s mi=miold
 	.//识别前处理上机信息
 	.//取出第一位命令类型
 	.s type=$p(record,"|",1)
 	.//解析EQU命令
 	.i type="EQU" d
 	..//前处理Seen命令
 	..s commandchild=$p($p(record,"|",3),"^",7)
 	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"前处理命令为:"_commandchild,"H<--M")
 	.//解析SAC命令
 	.i type="SAC" d
 	..//解析上前处理信息
 	..//取出流水号
 	..s epis=$p(record,"|",5)
 	..//取出前处理或仪器信息
 	..s machCode=$p(record,"|",11)
 	..//取出位置信息
 	..s positioninfo=$p(record,"|",12)
 	..//----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->根据前处理命令处理
 	..i commandchild="SEEN" d //自动核收
 	...//得到当前工作小组
 	...s curWorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
 	...s CurWorkGroupDR=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(curWorkGroupMachineDR),4)
 	...s curMachName=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),5)
 	...//得到仪器工作小组的核收类型
 	...s AcceptFlag=$lg($g(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(curWorkGroupMachineDR)),13)
 	...//如果是前处理小组，就认为上前处理
 	...//************************************************************************************************
 	...i AcceptFlag="1"  d
 	....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"上前处理，鉴定号:"_epis_"的标本在:"_curMachName_",样本所在:"_positioninfo,"H<--M")
 	....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"执行核收到前处理","H<--M")
 	....//此处核收医嘱导前处理工作小组，不生成项目，写标本操作日志
 	....s dealret=##Class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).PreDealLabNo(mi,epis,"") 
 	....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"核收到前处理返回信息:"_dealret,"H<--M")
 	....//记录位置信息到报告位置号
 	....d ..SaveRackNo(epis,positioninfo,mi)
 	....i dealret["标本已核收" q 
 	....i dealret="1" d
 	.....//写标本操作日志
 	.....d ..SaveRecord(epis,machCode,mi,"5")
 	....e  d
 	.....s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    .....s perUser = "WG-"_CurWorkGroupDR
    .....s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": """", ""info"": """_epis_"前处理核收失败:"_dealret_",仪器【"_curMachName_"】！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
 	.....//写标本操作日志
 	.....d ..SaveRecord(epis,dealret,mi,"100")
 	.....//************************************************************************************************
 	...e  d
 	....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"上仪器，鉴定号:"_epis_"的标本在:"_curMachName_",样本所在:"_positioninfo,"H<--M")
 	....//核收操作，记录位置号5984@1
 	....//标本操作，类型：已上机，备注：C8000A 5984@1
 	....//上机提示（仪器项目上传日志，增加流水号索引）
 	....//此处调核收逻辑核收到仪器，标本从前处理小组进入仪器的小组
 	....s dealret=##Class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).ReceiveLabNoByWGM(mi,epis,"","","LSHS") 
 	....;s RetLL=$$SaveLastMachine^MI.MIF000(mi,epis,"1")
    ....;d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,RetLL,"最后仪器")
 	....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"核收到仪器返回:"_dealret,"H<--M")
 	....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"执行记录位置号:"_positioninfo,"H<--M")
 	....//不管接收是否成功，记录位置信息到报告位置号
 	....d ..SaveRackNo(epis,"已上机:"_positioninfo,mi)
 	....d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"记录位置号完成","H<--M")
 	....i dealret["标本已核收" q 
 	....i dealret="1"  d
 	.....//写标本操作日志
 	.....d ..SaveRecord(epis,"仪器:"_curMachName_",位置:"_positioninfo_"核收",mi,"5")
 	.....d ..SaveRecord(epis,"已上流水线:"_positioninfo,mi,"5")
 	....e  d
 	.....s retObj=##Class(wbsLisMsgAsyncHandler.LISMsg.wbsLisMsgAsyncHandlerSoap).%New()
    .....s perUser = "WG-"_CurWorkGroupDR
    .....s ret=retObj.SendMsg("dhcc","{ ""type"": """", ""info"": """_epis_"前处理核收失败:"_dealret_",仪器【"_curMachName_"】！"_""", ""dealurl"": """" }", "Crisis", perUser)
 	.....//写标本操作日志
 	.....d ..SaveRecord(epis,dealret,mi,"100")
 	..//----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->根据前处理命令处理
 	..i commandchild="RESULT" d //处理分类信息
 	...//通过仪器对照码取仪器
 	...s curMachName=machCode
 	...//此处存标本全部审核报告的位置号
 	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"分类信息，标本号:"_epis_"的样本所在仪器:"_curMachName_" "_positioninfo,"H<--M")
 	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"执行记录分类信息:"_positioninfo,"H<--M")
 	...//保存分类信息到架子号
 	...d ..SaveCARCH(epis,curMachName_": "_positioninfo,mi,curMachName)
 	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"记录分类信息完成","H<--M")
 	...//写标本操作日志
 	...d ..SaveRecord(epis,"上机位置:"_positioninfo,mi,"6")
 	..//----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->根据前处理命令处理
 	..i commandchild="ARCHIVE" d //处理归档信息
 	...//通过仪器对照码取仪器
 	...s curMachName=machCode
 	...//此处存标本全部审核报告的位置号
 	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"归档信息，标本号:"_epis_"的样本所在仪器:"_curMachName_" "_positioninfo,"H<--M")
 	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"执行记录分类信息:"_positioninfo,"H<--M")
 	...//保存归档信息到架子号
 	...d ..SaveCARCH(epis,"归档:"_positioninfo,mi,"归档")
 	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"记录归档信息完成","H<--M")
 	...//写标本操作日志
 	...d ..SaveRecord(epis,"归档位置:"_positioninfo,mi,"101")
 	.//----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->处理结果数据
 	.//解析质控数据,P业务数据，Q质控数据
 	
 	.i (type["MSH") d
 	..s ^TMP("RS600",mi,"MSH")=$p(record,"|",10)
 	..//取日期串
 	..s DateStr=$p(record,"|",7)
 	..//解析保存日期串
 	..i $l(DateStr)=14 s ^TMP("RS600",mi,"DATE")=$e(DateStr,1,8)_","_(($e(DateStr,9,10)*3600)+($e(DateStr,11,12)*60))
 	.i type="OBR" s ^TMP("RS600",mi,"OBR")=$p(record,"|",3)
 	.i type="ORC" s ^TMP("RS600",mi,"ORC")=$p(record,"|",3)
 	.//仪器警告
 	.i type="NTE" d	
 	..s WaringStr=$p(record,"|",4)
 	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"仪器报警信息:"_WaringStr,"H<--M")
 	..s WaringCode=$p(WaringStr," ",2)
 	..i $l(WaringCode) d
 	...i WaringCode="5" s WaringStr=">ABS(超出ABS)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="43" s WaringStr="Cal.E(校准结果异常)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="2" s WaringStr=">Cuvet(反应杯空白异常)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="42" s WaringStr="Edit(实验结果已被编辑)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="23" s WaringStr=">ISE(超出ISE范围)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="19" s WaringStr="ISE.E(ISE电压级错误)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="56" s WaringStr=">Kin(Prozone错误2/运动不稳)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="10" s WaringStr=">Lin(线性异常)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="11" s WaringStr=">Lin(线性异常)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="6" s WaringStr=">Prozone(Prozone错误1)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="4" s WaringStr="Reag.S(试剂不足)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="44" s WaringStr=">Rept(高出原倍复查范围)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="45" s WaringStr="<Rept(低于原倍复查范围)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="46" s WaringStr="Samp.？(高出ABS最大值)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="68" s WaringStr="Samp.B(样本中有气泡)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="72" s WaringStr="Samp.C(样本中有凝块)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="26" s WaringStr=">Test(高出线性范围)"
 	...e  i WaringCode="27" s WaringStr="<Test(低于线性范围)"
 	..//保存仪器报警信息到组内报告评价
 	..d ..SaveResultWarned(epis,WaringStr,mi)
 	.d ##class(MI.Special.RecordGlobal).RecordData(epis,recordbak,"MI.MIFRS600",1,10)	//YHR 20230828 记录十天的数据
 	.i type="OBX" d
 	..s (sample,result,date,time,QC)=""
 	..s epis=^TMP("RS600",mi,"OBR")
 	..s machCode=$p($p($p($p(record,"|",16),"^",1),":",1),"^",1)
 	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"解析仪器对照码:"_machCode,"H<--M")
 	..//通过仪器对照码取仪器
 	..s code=$p($p(record,"|",4),"^",1) ;AHBS^6012
 	..s reswaring=$p($p(record,"|",6),"^",2)
 	..s res=$p($p(record,"|",6),"^",1) ;[""一般|-1阴性+定量|1阳性+定量|0临界值]
 	..s CallThePolice=$p($p(record,"|",9),"^",2)
 	..i $l(CallThePolice) d
 	...try{d ..SaveAlarmInformation(mi,epis,CallThePolice)}catch {} //YHR 20230828 保存报警信息
 	..//i res=-1 s res="阴性"_$c(92)_$p($p(record,"|",6),"^",2)_$c(92)_$c(92)_reswaring
 	..//e  i res=1 s res="阳性"_$c(92)_$p($p(record,"|",6),"^",2)_$c(92)_$c(92)_reswaring
 	..//e  i res=0 s res="临界值"_$c(92)_$p($p(record,"|",6),"^",2)_$c(92)_$c(92)_reswaring
 	..//e  s res="临界值"_$c(92)_$c(92)_$c(92)_reswaring
 	..i res="SORTED" q
 	..i res="N/I" q
 	..//标本质量数据当做仪器报警，不让自动审核
 	..i code="SQ-D" d
 	...//保存仪器报警信息到报告评价
 	...//d ..SaveResultWarned(epis,res,mi)
 	...d ..SaveQuality(epis,res,mi)
 	..//计算肾小球滤过率
 	..i code="8690" d
 	...s x1="Cur"
 	...s x2=##class(MI.Special.GetSxqlgl).GeteGFRResultLast(mi,epis,res)
 	...i $l(x2) s result=result_x1_$c(92)_x2_$c(44)
 	..s result=result_code_$c(92)_res_$c(44) 	
 	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_":"_result,"H<--M")
 	..d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,"按对照仪器保存数据:"_machCode,"H<--M")
 	..//统一保存结果
 	..i $l(epis),$l(result) d
 	...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,epis_"$$"_result,"H<--M")
 	...s DateStr=""
 	...i $d(^TMP("RS600",mi,"DATE")) s DateStr=^TMP("RS600",mi,"DATE")
 	...i $l(DateStr) d
 	....s date=$p(DateStr,",",1)
 	....s time=$p(DateStr,",",2)
 	...d ##Class(MI.Common.MIFBase).Save(mi, epis, result, date, time, QC)
	q "1"
}

ClassMethod SaveRecord(labno, OperateNotes, mi, OperateTypeCode)
{
	s labno=$g(labno)
	s OperateNotes=$g(OperateNotes)
	s mi=$g(mi)
	s OperateTypeCode=$g(OperateTypeCode)
	s curWorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)),6)
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno))) d
	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	.//标本ID,操作时间,操作者,操作说明,操作类型,工作组,标本拒收类型

	.d ##class(HIS.DHCCommon).SaveRecord(VisitNumberDR,$zd($h,8),$p($h,",",2),"",OperateNotes,OperateTypeCode,curWorkGroupMachineDR,"")
}

// D ##class(MI.MIFRS600).SaveResultWarned("","")

ClassMethod SaveResultWarned(labno, conclusion, predealMI)
{
	s labno=$g(labno)
	s conclusion=$g(conclusion)
	s predealMI=$g(predealMI)
	s curWorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(predealMI)),6)
	s hasFindRep=0
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno))) d
	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR)) d
	..s WorkGroupMachineDR="" f  s WorkGroupMachineDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WorkGroupMachineDR)) q:WorkGroupMachineDR=""  d
	...s OrderNo="" f  s OrderNo=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WorkGroupMachineDR,OrderNo)) q:OrderNo=""  d
	....s ReportDR="" f  s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR,WorkGroupMachineDR,OrderNo,ReportDR)) q:ReportDR=""  d
	.....s Status=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),22) 
	.....i Status="3" q
	.....s WorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportD(ReportDR)),4) 
	.....s objrep=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReport).%OpenId(ReportDR)
	.....i $l(objrep.ResultWarned) s objrep.ResultWarned=objrep.ResultWarned_","_conclusion
	.....e  s objrep.ResultWarned=conclusion
	.....s sc=objrep.%Save()
	.....s hasFindRep=1
	.....i ('$SYSTEM.Status.IsOK(sc)) d
	......d Trace^MI.MIF000(predealMI,"-1^存仪器报警信息失败:"_$SYSTEM.Status.GetErrorText(sc),"H<--M")
	i hasFindRep=0,$l(curWorkGroupMachineDR),$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",$zd($h,8),curWorkGroupMachineDR,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno))) d
	.s ReportDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexEpisodeNo",$zd($h,8),curWorkGroupMachineDR,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	.s objrep=##Class(dbo.RPVisitNumberReport).%OpenId(ReportDR)
	.s objrep.ResultWarned=conclusion
	.s sc=objrep.%Save()
	.s hasFindRep=1
	i hasFindRep=0 d Trace^MI.MIF000(predealMI,labno_":没有找到报告","H<--M")
	q "1"
}

ClassMethod SaveQuality(labno, conclusion, predealMI)
{
	s labno=$g(labno)
	s conclusion=$g(conclusion)
	s predealMI=$g(predealMI)
	s curWorkGroupMachineDR=$lg($g(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(predealMI)),6)
	s hasFindRep=0
	i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno))) d
	.s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(labno),""))
	.i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR)) d

ClassMethod QryLabInfoExecute(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, mi As %String, P1, P2, P3, P4, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %Status
{
    Set repid=$i(^CacheTemp)

    s mi=$g(mi),flag=$g(flag)
    i '$d(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(mi)) q ""
    s LabnoList=""

    //*-------------------------------->*申请项目

    s AddDate=$zd($p($h,",",1)-2,8) f  s AddDate=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData("U"),AddDate)) q:AddDate=""  d
    .s AddTime="" f  s AddTime=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData("U"),AddDate,AddTime)) q:AddTime=""  d
    ..s MiUploadDR=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData("U"),AddDate,AddTime,""))
    ..b ;F101
    ..s labno=$lg(^dbo.RPMachineUploadD(MiUploadDR),3)
    ..;s EpisNo=$$getEpis^MI.MIF000(labno,mi)
    ..;i '$l(EpisNo) q
    ..i '$l(labno) q
    ..b ;12
    ..i $l(labno) S VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",labno,""))
    ..b ;VisitNumberDR
    ..i '$l(VisitNumberDR) q
    ..i '$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR)) q
    ..//得到通道号

    ...s labnoInfo=labno_","_$replace(TCList,"\","+")_"|@U"
    ...s txtInfo=..GetLabnoInfoN(mi,labnoInfo,patInfo)
    ...s now=$now()
    ...s filenametime=$zd($p(now,",",1),8)_$tr($zt($p(now,",",2)),":")_$p(now,".",2)
    ...s filename=filenametime_"_"_labno_".hl7"

    ...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,txtInfo,"上传信息")
    ...d OutputRow
    ...//文本双向上传结束******************************************************
    //*-------------------------------->*取消项目
    s AddDate=$zd($p($h,",",1)-1,8) f  s AddDate=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData("R"),AddDate)) q:AddDate=""  d
    .s AddTime="" f  s AddTime=$o(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexSendStatus",mi,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData("R"),AddDate,AddTime)) q:AddTime=""  d

    ..s labno=$lg(^dbo.RPMachineUploadD(MiUploadDR),3)
    ..;s EpisNo=$$getEpis^MI.MIF000(labno,mi)
    ..;i '$l(EpisNo) q
    ..i '$l(labno) q
    ..b ;12
    ..i $l(labno) S VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",labno,""))
    ..b ;VisitNumberDR
    ..i '$l(VisitNumberDR) q
    ..;i '$d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportI("IndexReportID",VisitNumberDR)) q
    ..//得到通道号
    ..s chl=$lg($g(^dbo.RPMachineUploadD(MiUploadDR)),7) 
    ..s patInfo=..GetPatInfo(mi,labno)
    ..s PatName=$p(patInfo,",",10)
    ..//测试类型0：文本，1：数据库
    ..s TestType="0"
    ..i TestType="0" d
    ...//文本双向上传开始******************************************************
    ...//控制输出文本的内容
    ...s labnoInfo=..GetLabnoInfo(mi,labno)_"@R"
    ...s txtInfo=..GetLabnoInfoN(mi,labnoInfo,patInfo)
    ...s now=$now()
    ...s filenametime=$zd($p(now,",",1),8)_$tr($zt($p(now,",",2)),":")_$p(now,".",2)
    ...s filename=filenametime_"_"_labno_".hl7"
    ...s Data=##class(MI.Common.MIFBase).DemoMOutFileInfo(filename,txtInfo,labno,1,"")
    ...d Trace^MI.MIF000(mi,txtInfo,"上传信息")
    ...d OutputRow
    ...//文本双向上传结束******************************************************
    Set qHandle=$lb(0,repid,0)
    Quit $$$OK
    
    
OutputRow
    Set ColFields="labno,labnoInfo,patInfo"
    Set ^CacheTemp(repid,ind)=##Class(LIS.Util.Common).TransListNull(Data,ColFields)
    Set ind=ind+1
    quit
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoClose(ByRef qHandle As %Binary) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Kill ^CacheTemp(repid)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod QryLabInfoFetch(ByRef qHandle As %Binary, ByRef Row As %List, ByRef AtEnd As %Integer = 0) As %Status [ PlaceAfter = QryLabInfoExecute ]
{
    Set AtEnd=$LIST(qHandle,1)
    Set repid=$LIST(qHandle,2)
    Set ind=$LIST(qHandle,3)
    Set ind=$o(^CacheTemp(repid,ind))
    If ind="" { 
        Set AtEnd=1
        Set Row=""
    }
    Else      { 
        Set Row=^CacheTemp(repid,ind)
    }
    s qHandle=$lb(AtEnd,repid,ind)
    Quit $$$OK
}

ClassMethod Upload(Labno, TestSetDR, WorkGroupMachineDR) As %String
{
	s Labno=$g(Labno),TestSetDR=$g(TestSetDR),WorkGroupMachineDR=$g(WorkGroupMachineDR)
	i '$l(Labno) q 100
	i '$l(TestSetDR),'$l(WorkGroupMachineDR) q 100

	s VisitNumberDR=$o(^dbo.RPVisitNumberI("IndexVisitNumber",##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Labno),""))
	I $L(WorkGroupMachineDR) d
	.D UploadTC 
	E  D //不传工作小组时遍历关联的所有主动上传仪器
	.S LinkWGMDR="" F  S LinkWGMDR=$O(^dbo.BTTestSetWorkGroupMachineI("IndexMaster",TestSetDR,LinkWGMDR)) Q:LinkWGMDR=""  D
	..S WorkGroupMachineDR=LinkWGMDR
	..//标本接收医院
	..s VisHosDR=$LG($G(^dbo.RPVisitNumberD(VisitNumberDR)),78)
	..//工作小组所在医院
	..s CKWGDR=$LG($G(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(LinkWGMDR)),4) 
	..s CkDepartDR=$LG($G(^dbo.BTWorkGroupD(CKWGDR)),4) 
	..S CkHosDR=$LG($G(^dbo.BTDepartmentD(CkDepartDR)),4) 
	..I CkHosDR'=VisHosDR Q //非本医院标本不生成工单
	..D UploadTCN
	q 1
UploadTC
	s CommDirection=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),11)
	///临时处理老年医院流水线标本上传
	//i CommDirection'="UP",CommDirection'="LS" s ^DHCUploadAll(Labno)=WorkGroupMachineDR

/// Creator：      杨浩然
/// CreatDate：    20230714
/// Description:： 主动上传生成项目工单
/// Table：        
/// Input：        标本号，工作小组ID，报告ID，项目ID主键，工单类型（R 删除，U 复查，C 增加）
/// Output：       成功1
/// Return：       生成上传工单 
/// Others         w ##class(LIS.Common.DHCVisitNumber).GenerateUploadRecordMTHD("1000100990","67","59396","^61^284","U")
ClassMethod GenerateUploadRecordMTHD(Labno, WorkGroupMachineDR, ReportDR, RepeatTCList, SendStatus, P5, P6, P7, P8, P9, P10, P11, P12, P13, Sessions, Output RowCount As %String) As %String
{
	s Labno=$g(Labno),WorkGroupMachineDR=$G(WorkGroupMachineDR)
	s ^TMP("CreateUploadRecordMTHD")=$LB(Labno, WorkGroupMachineDR)
    s Labno=$g(Labno),ReportDR=$g(ReportDR),WorkGroupMachineDR=$g(WorkGroupMachineDR),RepeatTCList=$g(RepeatTCList),SendStatus=$g(SendStatus)
	i '$l(Labno) q 100
	i '$l(ReportDR) q 100 
	i '$l(WorkGroupMachineDR) q 100
	i '$l(SendStatus) q 100
	s CommDirection=$lg(^dbo.BTWorkGroupMachineD(WorkGroupMachineDR),11)
	///临时处理老年医院流水线标本上传
	//i CommDirection'="UP",CommDirection'="LS" s ^DHCUploadAll(Labno)=WorkGroupMachineDR
	i CommDirection'="UP",CommDirection'="LS" q 100
	s ret=100
	s TCList=""
	s MachineDR="" 
	f  s MachineDR=$o(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterI("IndexWorkGroupMachine",WorkGroupMachineDR,MachineDR)) q:MachineDR=""  d
	.;i $d(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexMaster",MachineDR,Labno)) q
	.s miCommDirection=$lg(^dbo.BTMIMachineParameterD(MachineDR),11)
	.i miCommDirection'="UP",CommDirection'="LS" q
    .f i=1:1:$l(RepeatTCList,"^") d
	..s TestCodeID=$p(RepeatTCList,"^",i)
	..i TestCodeID="" q
	..//如果是复查或者删除项目则判断该项目是不是该报告的
	..i (SendStatus="U")||(SendStatus="R") d
    ...i $d(^dbo.RPVisitNumberReportResultI("IndexReportItem",ReportDR,TestCodeID)) d
    ....i $d(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeI("IndexUPChannel",MachineDR,TestCodeID)) d
	.....s UPChannel=$o(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeI("IndexUPChannel",MachineDR,TestCodeID,""))
	.....i UPChannel=-100000000000000 q
	.....b ;102
	.....s TCList=TCList_UPChannel_"\"
	..e  i SendStatus="C" d
	...i $d(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeI("IndexUPChannel",MachineDR,TestCodeID)) d
	....s UPChannel=$o(^dbo.BTMIMachineTestCodeI("IndexUPChannel",MachineDR,TestCodeID,""))
	....i UPChannel=-100000000000000 q
	....b ;102
	....s TCList=TCList_UPChannel_"\"
	.b ;101
	.s TCList=$e(TCList,1,$l(TCList)-1)
	.i '$l(TCList) s ret=Labno_"没有上传项目" q 
	.S RowID=""
  	.i $d(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexMaster",MachineDR,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Labno))) s RowID=$O(^dbo.RPMachineUploadI("IndexMaster",MachineDR,##Class(LIS.Util.Common).IndexData(Labno),""))
	.I $L(RowID) s obj=##class(dbo.RPMachineUpload).%OpenId(RowID)
	.e  s obj=##class(dbo.RPMachineUpload).%New()
	.s obj.MachineParameterDR=MachineDR
	.s obj.VisitNumber=Labno
	.s obj.SendStatus=SendStatus
	.s obj.AddDate=$tr($zd(+$h,3),"-")
	.s obj.AddTime=$p($h,",",2)
	.s obj.TCList=TCList
	.s ret=obj.%Save()
	Q ret
}
